    "id": "f_csv_fd085b850b",
    "slug": "we-who-are-like-senseless-children-shrink-from-suffering-but-love-its-causes-w",
    "texto": "We who are like senseless children shrink from suffering, but love its causes. We hurt ourselves; our pain is self-inflicted! Why should others be the object of our anger?",
    "autor": "Śāntideva",
    "autorSlug": "santideva",
